&lt;li&gt;captant.lbr
&lt;li&gt;polcap.lbr
&lt;li&gt;ipc-smd.lbr
&lt;/ul&gt;
All SMD packages are defined according to the IPC specifications and  CECC&lt;p&gt;
&lt;author&gt;Created by librarian@cadsoft.de&lt;/author&gt;&lt;p&gt;
